  "body": "This is not a bug - just opening and closing in case anyone else is searching this error. \r\n\r\nI often alias `npm test` to a shell script (stolen from Zeppelin) that spins up ganache in the background, executes the test command and shuts ganache down when it's done.  Buidler sometimes launches so fast that ganache isn't ready to accept calls when the tests begin and this error appears. \r\n```\r\nError: connect ECONNREFUSED 127.0.0.1:8545\r\n    at TCPConnectWrap.afterConnect [as oncomplete] (net.js:1097:14)\r\n```\r\nWorkaround : add a `sleep 5` between client launch and test command. ",
